a%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoved-from-the-us-to-wales-fourteen-years-ago-2025-9%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emoved%20to%20Wales%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20has%20made%20Cardiff%20my%20home%20for%20the%20last%20two%20decades.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIn%20the%20city%20center%2C%20you%20can%20explore%20a%20castle%2C%20watch%20a%20rugby%20game%2C%20or%20walk%20around%20a%20park.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ECardiff%20is%20compact%2C%20easy%20to%20navigate%2C%20and%20full%20of%20friendly%20people.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EGrowing%20up%2C%20I%20never%20even%20really%20wanted%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbucket-list-trip-london-tourist-activities-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Evisit%20the%20United%20Kingdom%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Naturally%2C%20I've%20ended%20up%20living%20here%20for%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20an%20American%20who%20has%20made%20the%20capital%20of%20Wales%20my%20home%20for%20the%20past%20two%20decades%2C%20and%20I'm%20not%20sorry%20I%20did.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECardiff%20is%20a%20vibrant%2C%20eclectic%2C%20and%20welcoming%20place.%20And%20it's%20relatively%20affordable%20compared%20to%20some%20other%20major%20cities%20in%20the%20UK.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20all%20its%20charm%2C%20the%20city%20doesn't%20pretend%20to%20be%20something%20it's%20not.%20Cardiff%20lures%20you%20in%20with%20its%20cheery%2C%20unassuming%20character%20and%20leaves%20you%20asking%20how%20anyone%20could've%20ever%20overlooked%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere%20are%20a%20few%20more%20reasons%20it%20deserves%20a%20spot%20on%20your%20travel%20list.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThere's%20a%20castle%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20city.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Cardiff%20Castle%20entrance%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6904c48e0be9845f2dc578a8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECardiff%20Castle%3Cp%3EJennifer%20Burns%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWales%20has%20more%20than%20400%20castles%20still%20standing%20or%20in%20ruins%20%E2%80%94%20more%20per%20square%20mile%20than%20any%20other%20country%20in%20Europe.%20One%20of%20them%20is%20in%20the%20center%20of%20Cardiff.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feuropean-cities-to-visit-places-to-skip-from-frequent-traveler%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ECardiff%20Castle%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20once%20the%20site%20of%20a%20Roman%20fort%2C%20has%20a%20history%20that%20spans%20about%202%2C000%20years%20(the%20remnants%20of%20its%20Roman%20origins%20are%20still%20visible%20within%20its%20walls).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEvery%20summer%2C%20you%20can%20go%20to%20gigs%20headlined%20by%20some%20of%20music's%20biggest%20artists%20or%20watch%20movies%20on%20an%20open-air%20screen%20in%20the%20impressive%20castle%20gardens.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJust%20bring%20a%20waterproof%20jacket%2C%20because%20the%20weather%20in%20Wales%20is%20nothing%20if%20not%20changeable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAnd%20there's%20a%20stadium%20across%20the%20street%20from%20it.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Stadium%20on%20edge%20of%20water%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6904c48e0be9845f2dc578a9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EJennifer%20Burns%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20into%20sports%2C%20Cardiff%20also%20has%20a%2070%2C000-seater%20stadium%20in%20its%20center%2C%20unusual%20for%20a%20European%20city.%20The%20energy%20in%20the%20area%20on%20a%20match%20day%20is%20astonishing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20you%20can%20cheer%20on%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcory-hill-wales-rugby-player-trashed-strangers-home-drunken-rage-2021-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EWales%20rugby%20team%20%3C%2Fa%3Eand%20then%20pick%20any%20number%20of