2%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F690e391521c3f142ebfc5509%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221800%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EYinka%20Ogunsunlade%20is%20a%20full-time%20attorney%20by%20day%20and%20a%20six-figure%20entrepreneur%20by%20night.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Yinka%20Ogunsunlade%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EYinka%20Ogunsunlade%20built%20a%20six-figure%20eBay%20side%20hustle%20over%20the%20last%2020%20years.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20started%20reselling%20items%20as%20a%20law%20student%2C%20with%20the%20goal%20of%20earning%20enough%20to%20pay%20his%20phone%20bill.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHis%20business%2C%20Fashionably%20Legal%2C%20now%20earns%20%24120%2C000%20a%20year%2C%20providing%20%26quot%3Ba%20double%20salary.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EYinka%20Ogunsunlade's%20earliest%20eBay%20memory%20is%20bidding%20on%20a%20watch%20as%20a%20teen.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20one%20of%20those%20cubic%20zirconia%20style%20watches%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BI%20won%20the%20auction%20and%20actually%20went%20to%20the%20post%20office%2C%20got%20a%20money%20order%2C%20and%20put%20it%20in%20the%20mail.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOgunsunlade%2C%20who%20grew%20up%20in%20Maryland%2C%20frequented%20eBay%20throughout%20high%20school%20and%20college%3A%20%26quot%3BI%20bought%20hundreds%20and%20hundreds%20of%20items%20%E2%80%94%20football%20jerseys%2C%20basketball%20jerseys.%20Jerseys%20were%20kind%20of%20all%20the%20rage%20in%20those%20early%202000s.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20wasn't%20until%20he%20was%20home%20for%20the%20holidays%20during%20his%20first%20year%20of%20law%20school%20in%202005%20that%20he%20considered%20listing%20items%20as%20a%20seller.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20mom%20always%20got%20the%20most%20Christmas%20gifts.%20She%20always%20had%20excess%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20recalled.%20That%20particular%20year%2C%20she%20received%20a%20perfume%20set%20she%20wasn't%20going%20to%20use.%20Out%20of%20curiosity%2C%20he%20listed%20it%20on%20eBay.%20%26quot%3BI%20sold%20that%20item%20fairly%20quickly%2C%20and%20thought%2C%20'If%20I%20can%20sell%20something%20I%20know%20nothing%20about%2C%20I'm%20sure%20I%20can%20sell%20items%20that%20I%20know%20a%20lot%20about.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20started%20listing%20items%20from%20his%20own%20closet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20was%20no%20start-up%20cost%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20meaning%20anything%20he%20sold%20was%20pure%20profit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20working%20his%20way%20through%20his%20closet%20items%2C%20Ogunsunlade%20needed%20to%20source%20inventory%20if%20he%20wanted%20to%20continue%20reselling%20on%20eBay.%20Having%20received%20%26quot%3Bthe%20shopping%20gene%20from%20my%20mom%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20there%20was%20a%20simple%20solution%3A%20%26quot%3BI%20love%20to%20shop%2C%20I%20love%20the%20thrill%20of%20the%20hunt%2C%20so%20I%20was%20like%2C%20let%20me%20go%20to%20these%20stores%20and%20see%20if%20I%20can%20find%20something%20to%20sell.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22878%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22yinka%20Ogunsunlade%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F690e3a1a513c94655a3dd988%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22659%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOgunsunlade%20is%20an%20attorney%20by%20trade%2C%20specializing%20in%20risk%20and%20compliance.%3Cp%3EMichaela%20Joy%20Photography%2FMichaela%20Joy%20Photography%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2235f14266-8c67-411a-905a-a847d88a0d96%5C%22%3EFrom%20bringing%20in%20enough%20to%20cover%20his%20cellphone%20bill%20to%20building%20a%20six-figure%20business%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThroughout%20law%20school%2C%20Ogunsunlade%20had%20two%20go-to%20stores%20for%20sourcing%20deals%3A%20Neiman%20Marcus%20Last%20Call%20and%20Saks%20OFF%205th.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20ensure%20he%20could%20turn%20a%20profit%2C%20he'd%20spend%20time%20browsing%20apparel%20and%20take%20photos%20of%20items%20along%20with%20their%20price%20tags.%20Then%2C%20he'd%20drive%20home%2C%20pull%20up%20eBay%20on%20his%20computer%20to%20look%20for%20what%20similar%20items%20sold%20for%2C%20and%20return%20to%20the%20department%20stores%20to%20buy%20the%20ones%20with%20the%20best%20profit%20margins.%20Finally%2C%20after%20buying%20the%20items%2C%20he'd%20take%20photos%20and%20list%20them%20on%20eBay%20with%20a%20detailed%20description.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThen%2C%20it's%20in%20the%20eyes%20of%20millions%20of%20people%20around%20the%20world%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Ogunsunlade%2C%20noting%20that%20his%20process%20is%20much%20more%20streamlined%20today.%20Thanks%20to%20smartphones%20and%20the%20eBay%20app%2C%20he%20can%20price-compare%20while%20shopping.%20He%20also%20sources%20items%20online%20now%2C%20which%20saves%20him%20time%20and%20gas%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20initial%20goal%20was%20to%20earn%20enough%20from%20eBay%20to%20cover%20one%20monthly%20bill.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20law%20student%2C%20%26quot%3Bevery%20sale%20counts%2C%20whether%20it%20be%20%2430%2C%20%245%2C%20or%20%2410%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20While%20his%20sales%20fluctuated%20throughout%20his%20first%20few%20years%20on%20the%20platform%2C%20he%20brought%20in%20enough%20each%20month%20to%20pay%20his%20cellphone%20bill.%20%26quot%3BThat%20was%20a%20light%20bulb%20moment%3A%20The%20money%20that%20I%20make%20doing%20something%20that%20I%20enjoy%20%E2%80%94%20searching%20for%20and%20buying%20items%20%E2%80%94%20can%20alleviate%20some%20of%20my%20expenses.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFrom%20there%2C%20Ogunsunlade%20set%20a%20goal%20to%20grow%20his%20side%20hustle%20income%20every%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221881%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Yinka%20Ogunsunlade%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F690e39d4513c94655a3dd976%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221411%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOgunsunlade%20started%20reselling%20items%20on%20eBay%20in%202005.%20Today%2C%20his%20business%2C%20Fashionably%20Legal%2C%20generates%20six%20figures%20in%20revenue.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Yinka%20Ogunsunlade%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20listing%20his%20first%20item%2020%20years%20ago%2C%20he%20has%20gradually%20built%20a%20six-figure%20reselling%20business%2C%20which%20he%20named%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3D206154102bfd2ecf051ccf2ba67d4a1e2f8e44089f199743dbd6d362cce08dcf%26postID%3D690e06cafe3b08067880ff87%26postSlug%3Debay-side-hustle-six-figures-lawyer-fashionably-legal-entrepreneurship-2025-11%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.ebay.com%252Fstr%252Ffashionablylegal%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFashionably%20Legal%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Between%20September%202024%20and%20September%202025%2C%20he%20did%20%24120%2C000%20in%20sales%20on%20eBay%2C%20according%20to%20a%20screenshot%20of%20his%20seller%20hub%20dashboard.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe's%20experimented%20with%20various%20product%20categories%2C%20including%20business%20attire%2C%20but%20has%20had%20the%20most%20success%20with%20athletic%20sneakers%20and%20apparel.%20It's%20the%20category%20he%20knows%20best.%20Plus%2C%20%26quot%3Beverybody's%20always%20going%20to%20need%20a%20pair%20of%20running%20shoes%20or%20walking%20shoes%20or%20less%20formal%2C%20athletic%20wear%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20more%20of%20an%20ebb%20and%20flow%20with%20the%20business%20attire%20category%3A%20%26quot%3BEspecially%20when%20COVID%20came%20around%2C%20people%20weren't%20going%20into%20the%20office%20and%20weren't%20even%20wearing%20business%20attire%2C%20so%20I%20saw%20a%20drop%20in%20people%20searching%20for%20neckties%20and%20formal%20wear%20online.%20I%20don't%20see%20those%20types%20of%20pronounced%20dips%20in%20the%20athletic%20market.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20pays%20attention%20to%20seasonal%20trends.%20At%20the%20start%20of%20football%20season%2C%20for%20example%2C%20he%20stocks%20up%20on%20cleats.%20He's%20learned%20that%2C%20%26quot%3Bonce%20July%20and%20August%20roll%20around%2C%20I%20know%20there's%20a%20parent%20somewhere%20in%20America%20with%20a%20kid%20that%20needs%20some%20football%20cleats.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EReselling%20on%20eBay%20is%20a%20time-intensive%20side%20hustle.%20Ogunsunlade%20estimates%20he%20spends%2030%20hours%20a%20week%20researching%2C%20sourcing%2C%20listing%2C%20and%20shipping%20items.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSometimes%20it's%20a%20grind%2C%20but%20the%20overall%20process%20is%20something%20that%20I%20enjoy%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20never%20seemed%20like%20work%20to%20me%2C%20and%20I%20never%20get%20burned%20out%20from%20listing%20items.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20extra%20income%20provides%20%26quot%3Ba%20double%20salary%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20It%20allowed%20him%20to%20take%20a%20year%20off%20from%20law%20when%20his%20son%20was%20born%20and%2C%20generally%2C%20provides%20financial%20peace%20of%20mind.%20%26quot%3BIt%20just%20changes%20your%20mental%20makeup%20%E2%80%94%20knowing%20that%20you%20don't%20have%20to%20rely%20specifically%20on%20a%209-to-5%20job%20that%20could%20end%20tomorrow.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Febay-side-hustle-six-figures-lawyer-fashionably-legal-entrepreneurship-2025-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1762683301000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F690e39487f37aa653f55a394%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Febay-side-hustle-six-figures-lawyer-fashionably-legal-entrepreneurship-2025-11%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Having%20a%20side%20hustle%20%26quot%3Bjust%20changes%20your%20mental%20makeup%20%E2%80%94%20knowing%20that%20you%20don't%20have%20to%20rely%20specifically%20on%20a%209-to-5%20job%20that%20could%20end%20tomorrow.%26quot%3B%22%2C