e28%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EZone%202%20builds%20stamina%20and%20heart%20health%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20foundation%20of%20longevity%20fitness%20is%20the%20ability%20to%20keep%20up%20a%20slow%2C%20steady%20effort%20over%20time.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20key%20here%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-is-zone-2-cardio-exercise-training-benefits-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EZone%202%20cardio%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20exercising%20at%2060-70%25%20of%20your%20max%20effort%2C%20or%20a%20pace%20at%20which%20you%20can%20hold%20a%20conversation%20without%20getting%20out%20of%20breath.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EZone%202%20can%20help%20boost%20your%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvo2-max-explained-what-is-good-how-improve-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EVO2%20max%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20the%20measure%20of%20how%20efficiently%20your%20body%20can%20use%20oxygen%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%E2%80%94%20a%20key%20indicator%20of%20heart%20health%20and%20fitness%20linked%20to%20better%20longevity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20need%20to%20have%20a%20Zone%202%20base%2C%26quot%3B%20Sprouse%20said%2C%20to%20%26quot%3Bbuild%20the%20machinery%20that%20allows%20you%20to%20get%20fitter.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20short%20on%20time%2C%20aim%20%3Cs%3Et%3C%2Fs%3Eo%20spend%20about%2050%25%20of%20your%20exercise%20time%20doing%20Zone%202%20cardio%20so%20you're%20not%20missing%20out%20on%20the%20benefits.%20If%20you've%20more%20hours%20a%20week%20to%20exercise%2C%20aim%20for%2080%25%20at%20Zone%202%20and%2020%25%20at%20a%20higher%20intensity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224a9635e0-6cf1-4bee-a30d-f6f22d099ce1%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EInterval%20training%20raises%20your%20lactate%20threshold%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudy-hiit-short-workouts-boost-fitness-longevity-stroke-survival-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EShorter%2C%20highe